Reasoning: The paper focuses on image generation with a disentangled 3D representation, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR). The use of deep generative models and adversarial learning also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the application of the model to texture and shape interpolation and appearance transfer suggests a connection to multimedia (cs.MM).
